#. Plugin Name of the plugin
msgid "Cashu For WooCommerce"
msgstr "Cashu For WooCommerce"

#. Plugin URI of the plugin
msgid "https://github.com/robwoodgate/cashu-for-woocommerce"
msgstr "https://github.com/robwoodgate/cashu-for-woocommerce"

#. Description of the plugin
msgid ""
"This plugin adds a secure Cashu payment gateway to your WooCommerce store, "
"allowing you to receive bitcoin ecash payments to your lightning address."
msgstr ""
"Cette extension ajoute une passerelle de paiement Cashu sécurisée à votre "
"boutique WooCommerce, vous permettant de recevoir des paiements ecash en "
"bitcoin directement sur votre adresse Lightning."

#. Author of the plugin
msgid "Rob Woodgate"
msgstr "Rob Woodgate"

#. Author URI of the plugin
msgid "https://www.github.com/robwoodgate"
msgstr "https://www.github.com/robwoodgate"

